=== Description (EN)
The maximum price that can be charged for LPG is the import price according to the Price Control Order on Goods and Services (Maximum Price for LPG at Refinery Gate) (Amendment), 5768-2008. Since October 2012, the price of kerosene based on CIF is published on the Platts website. Therefore, 2 prices are published: 1. Kerosene price based on FOB plus the difference between the price of transport diesel FOB / CIF. 2. Price according to quotation.

