The database centralizes data on measured environmental impacts of materials and products, especially their carbon footprint. The data was measured using Life Cycle Assessment (LCA), verified by a qualified third party, and reported voluntarily by manufacturers and importers. The goals are to encourage transparency, enable environmentally preferable consumer choices, and create competition to reduce environmental impacts.

