=== Description (EN)
The Ministry of Environmental Protection, the Ministry of Agriculture, the Nature and Parks Authority, drainage authorities and stream authorities have jointly prepared to stop the continued spread of Ambrosia confertiflora. This invasive species causes damage to agriculture, wetlands, infrastructure, gardens and parks, and may even cause allergies in humans. In any case where Ambrosia confertiflora is observed, it should be reported to the Ministry of Environmental Protection's information center by phone: \*6911

