=== Description (EN)
Ecological mapping for mosquito control – point This layer presents the ecological value of aquatic habitats from a point source (springs, winter ponds, reservoirs, wastewater treatment plants, etc.) and provides a basis for implementing guidelines for mosquito control according to the level of ecological value. Ecological mapping for mosquito control – line This layer presents the ecological value of aquatic habitats from a linear source (streams, canals, drainage ditches, agricultural canals, etc.) and provides a basis for implementing guidelines for mosquito control according to the level of ecological value.

