=== Description (EN)
The database contains information regarding contaminated land sites. The information serves the public in recognizing the various pollution centers located in the State of Israel for various purposes: for example, professional factors in the financial field \\ valuation world - as information for the purpose of hedging risk, consulting companies - as background material for the purpose of formulating surveys, and for many additional purposes. The existing information contains general information about the site's activity, the administrative status of the site in terms of soil investigation and rehabilitation, update dates and information regarding the presence of soil gases and groundwater. There is no specific information regarding pollution levels.

