=== Description (EN)
A Knesset member may submit a query to a minister on a matter within the minister's area of responsibility. The query database contains regular and urgent queries submitted since the 19th Knesset and is updated regularly. The database allows searching by MK, status, dates, subject, and minister. It also includes the minister's response and additional questions asked in the plenum.

