=== Description (EN)
The Israel Land Authority hires licensed surveyors, independent firms, to perform mapping and surveying work. For this purpose, it operates a database of licensed surveyors who meet the professional requirements it has defined. The surveyors in the database perform a variety of types of surveying work according to the needs of the spatial mapping departments and the Parcelization and Land Settlement Division of the Authority.

