=== Description (EN)
The calculator and attached documents are a planning tool for assessing the supply and mix of parking for light transport vehicles (bicycles, electric scooters, etc.) at public transport hubs. The tool allows calculating the number of parking spaces required, the required designated area and the security levels according to the type of hub, passenger volumes, station characteristics and the urban environment.

