This dataset presents the planned trips of buses in public transportation each month: approved licensed trips, non-execution, advances, delays, regular trips, and unlicensed trips. The dataset is updated on the 1st of each month with data from the months that have passed since the beginning of the current calendar year, with a delay of 3 months.

