=== Description (EN)
Map of runoff recharge prioritization areas and GIS layer. The recharge prioritization areas were defined according to hydrogeological information as feeding areas of central aquifers, which are used by the water sector in Israel. These layers are intended for planners and planning institutions, for the purpose of preferring runoff management solutions that include recharge to groundwater.

