=== Description (EN)
The Senior Citizens Law states that a senior citizen is an Israeli resident who has reached retirement age according to the Population Registry. The retirement age today is 67 for men and 62 for women. A senior citizen card is sent to the senior citizen close to reaching retirement age, according to the Population Registry.

